Rules-Game Settings:
- Must be played on Black Label version (2002.10.07.BLACK VER);
- 1 Round Game;
- Only 1 credit at a time.

Multi-day Event Info:
First weekend:
{
   8 possible hanchan blocks, play in any 5.
   First starts at tournament start time, each other one is 1:15 later
   Top 16 by total score advance
}

Second weekend:
{
   Top 16 double elimination
   Finals is a game to West, with players coming from winners with a mangan advantage
}
